SETBACKS ARE SETUPS. 

With the NBA season quickly approaching, I had the opportunity to sit down with @KlayThompson to chop it up regarding his love of the game and his mindset after his comeback from rupturing his Achilles.

Trust me, I’ve been there and ruptured mine — it’s a devastating injury to battle back from. If you’re a hooper, you really know the mental fortitude it takes to not only overcome this injury physically, but more importantly to mentally get back to elite form. Team Achilles Rehab Crew, ha!! Salute brother — keep on letting it fly 🎯💯🎯

Always complete, never finished 💯 

First comes the vision, but most importantly the ability to execute. Blood, sweat & tears put into this brand platform. Most only see the end result, not all the years it took to build, sleepless nights, and everything else in b/t to get here. Lots more to do, but just grateful for all the people, relationships and community in and around the ACES ecosystem — it truly takes a village, ya’ll know who you are!🙏🏽 Oh, and one heck of a weekend for the 2023 Hustle & Hear™️ Classic featuring some of the top HS players in the country from @ote + @aces — that was one for books! 

If you’re building something of value, keep going day in & day out, it’s not a matter of “if” but only “when.” 🏁♠️

Side-note: The “Mecca ACES” collection celebrates the culture of basketball, and fight & grind in all of us. Stay tuned, dropping this afternoon on @aces + @dunk ‼️
